	<text xml:lang="de">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salve, mi venerande Bullingere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Longas literas Habii vestri caussa <placeName ref="l1050" cert="high">Stutgardiam</placeName> scripsi<note target="fn2" type="footnote"/>, si quo modo caussae illius adesse possim, quominus est, ut ad te pluribus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę in Wirtempergensium ecclesiarum ritibus desideras quęque mutata cupis, plane grato animo accepi<note target="fn3" type="footnote"/>; verum si, quo loco sim, diligentius tecum perpendas, facile intelliges, quo sint omnia facta consilio quove authore.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magnum videbar mihi impetrasse, postquam mea admonitione resecta sunt quędam longe iis superstitiosiora, quę nonnulli etiam extra Schnepfium affinxerant<note target="fn4" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Speramus domini beneficio solidiora aliquando daturos principes.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Minor catechismus plane is est, quem <persName ref="p514" cert="high">Brentius</persName> edidit<note target="fn5" type="footnote"/>, nec verbum mutatum, nisi quod ad calcem<note target="fn6" type="footnote"/> additę sunt preculae quedam, ne vacuę essent paginę.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alioqui noveram, quam variarent hic veteres.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><pb type="edition" next="297"/>Eleemosynarum dispensationem mitto<note target="fn7" type="footnote"/>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil praeterea possum ac vehementer immodicis istis occupationibus meis irascor, quę sic me sibi devinciunt, ut ab amicorum vel tumultuaria salutatione invitissimum revellant.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu, mi venerande frater, servatori Christo me meumque ministerium diligenter commenda.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta fratres, inprimis uxorem<note target="fn8" type="footnote"/>, <persName ref="p165" cert="high">Pellicanum</persName>, Leonem<note target="fn9" type="footnote"/>, <persName ref="p14" cert="high">Theodorum</persName><note target="fn10" type="footnote"/> etc.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iterum vale et per Christum ignosce brevitati.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="de" type="auto">21. maiii.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus Ambr. Blaur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p230" cert="high">Volmarius</persName> lavat in Ferinis Balneis<note target="fn11" type="footnote"/>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ubi redierit, reddam, quae misisti<note target="fn12" type="footnote"/>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
